% function that returns true or false = a predicate
% if we have a line with OR we write 2 separate lines(ex: if n==4 or n==7 we write N=4, N=7 separate)
% if we have a line with AND we write it together
% we have to return something!!! never return nothing 

% mult(L-list, K-number, R-result list)
% flow model(input,input,output)
% _ = unnamed general variable, []=empty list
% [H|T] = [Head(of the list)| Tail] - before | is a variable, after | is a list; all of this used to extract elements

mulk([], _, []).
mulk([H|T], K, R):-
  NewH is H*K,
  mulk(T, K, TR),
  R=[NewH|TR].
